---
name: HTML Rules
---

- Always include shared CSS in <head> in order: base, components, layout, themes, responsive.
- Always include theme-manager.js in <head>.
- Always include app.js before </body>.
- Use shared/templates/master-layout.html with placeholder variables ({{PAGE_TITLE}}, {{CSS_BASE_PATH}}, {{NAVIGATION_LINKS}}, {{CURRENT_PAGE}}).
- Never inline styles.
- Never duplicate nav, header, or sidebar markup.
- Wrap content with <main class="content-wrapper">.
